text: Diana Mason (29 April 1933 - 29 March 2016) was a British equestrian. She competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:2016 deaths Category:British female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Great Britain Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Solihull
